Separate from import reaction, because import doesn't use gene

move to apico (from mito); made irreversible

TPx2 is mito; remove one gene
copy; move to cyto (from mito); made irreversible
Only occurs during state of stress
Only occurs during state of stress
Only occurs during state of stress
Constant production of superoxide (from stress) creates stress - only force lower bound to be >0 for particular simulations
Export only or else glycolysis is unnecessary
Removed TCA association and extra genes
